lead_paragraph: Apartment-sharing startup Airbnb has taken bookings from more than 66,000 visitors coming to this month's Olympic Games in Rio de Janeiro, from upmarket seafront districts like Copacabana to the city's hillside slums, company officials said on Monday.

headline.print_headline: Airbnb Says More Tourists Still Booking for Rio Games
